7371 - Computer Programming Services Summary > MOODLE PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover computer programming services. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. MOODLE PTY LTD is headquartered in West Perth, Western Australia. It is headed by managing director & company secretary Martin Chris Dougiamas. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $35.21 million. Its net loss totalled $2.94 million. MOODLE PTY LTD forms part of the services industry sector.
